return ['messages'=>['0df2c9fdbd5deea1fb04c68c58db556b'=>'And how did I do it?','0f7349081cc29e835da3ee3f1cffd3c0'=>'It\'s everywhere, it\'s everything you see.','1eeedbb04fc5ae4c22452eabe8105264'=>'It multiplies with each new brand that decides to appear.','1f69feedfa7097648b58cd95f47f6683'=>'<strong>SHOWING MYSELF.</strong>','2235bb5598caf6e4db0327645acfa1e4'=>'Then I get into the vicious cycle of scratching my skin as a reflex out of anxiety, which creates even more marks, which creates even more anxiety...','2d9880d9a852e55c7730962e7e11e25d'=>'Those thousands of little marks that you see, that come and go, and walk around on my skin.','4cd16bbd8718dee89bb62b4ef83d3372'=>'A skin full of marks is not <strong>ONE</strong> insecurity, it is <strong>THOUSANDS</strong> at once. ','508283c142f4be568b5ea8b4065ecb7a'=>'To learn to have control, not only of myself or my body, <em>but of the way I look at myself.</em>','8d74df5da015e94af0f38e0af3a2f87c'=>'All that remains is to learn to live with it.','959215ff397f88931fec20f5cfdae9bd'=>'This is actually one of the main reasons why I started to self-retract, to learn to observe myself as I am. To learn to see myself from the outside, from an external perspective, but at the same time very much my own. ','97fe514525327a482daaa638c2a8b45c'=>'When your insecurity is your skin, tell me, how do you hide it?','<strong>MOSTRÁNDOME.</strong>'=>'<strong>SHOWING MYSELF.</strong>','Cuando tu inseguridad es tu piel, dime, ¿cómo la escondes?'=>'When your insecurity is your skin, tell me, how do you hide it?','Entonces entro en el círculo vicioso de rascar mi piel como reflejo de la ansiedad, lo cual, genera aún más marcas, lo cual genera aún más ansiedad...'=>'Then I get into the vicious cycle of scratching my skin as a reflex out of anxiety, which creates even more marks, which creates even more anxiety...','Esas miles de marquitas que ves, que vienen y van, y se pasean por mi piel.'=>'Those thousands of little marks that you see, that come and go, and walk around on my skin.','Esta es en realidad una de las principales razones por las que empecé a autorretrarme, para aprender a observarme tal cual soy. Para aprender a verme desde afuera, desde una visión ajena, pero a la vez muy mía.'=>'This is actually one of the main reasons why I started to self-retract, to learn to observe myself as I am. To learn to see myself from the outside, from an external perspective, but at the same time very much my own. ','Está en todos lados, es todo aquello que se ve.'=>'It\'s everywhere, it\'s everything you see.','Mi mayor inseguridad no es una sola, es el conjunto de muchas a la vez.'=>'My biggest insecurity is not just one, it is a combination of many at once.','Para aprender a tener el control, ya no de mí o de mi cuerpo, <em>sino de mi forma de mirarme.</em>'=>'To learn to have control, not only of myself or my body, <em>but of the way I look at myself.</em>','Se multiplica con cada marca nueva que decide aparecer.'=>'It multiplies with each new brand that decides to appear.','Solo queda aprender a vivir con ella.'=>'All that remains is to learn to live with it.','Una piel llena de marcas, no es <strong>UNA</strong> inseguridad, es <strong>MILES</strong> a la vez. '=>'A skin full of marks is not <strong>ONE</strong> insecurity, it is <strong>THOUSANDS</strong> at once. ','f7d5fda2f98119ed141ea1d4eadf3174'=>'My biggest insecurity is not just one, it is a combination of many at once.','¿Y cómo lo he hecho?'=>'And how did I do it?']];
